  "subject": "Create common/clients pom module",
  "commit_message": "Create common/clients pom module\n\n- create clients pom module\n- group clients and clients-base modules under this module\n- this prepares further splitting up the clients module for instance\n  to move the cds client [0] into it's own module which makes it easier\n  to exclude\n\n[0] which is pulling in tons of dependencies like various kotlin\n    and grpc deps\n\nIssue-ID: SO-4224\nChange-Id: Ia83b4ba70ebb16554fdf6217d035400fd5fe5627\nSigned-off-by: Fiete Ostkamp <Fiete.Ostkamp@telekom.de>\n",
